:43183,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting mixed group with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a mixed gathering of Muslims and Jews and he greeted them all with peace. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2702 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0651 \u0628\u0650\u0645\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/allah-displeased-if-no-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":43183,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah displeased with unmindful gatherings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit in a gathering without remembering Allah, or sending blessings upon their Prophet, but that they will earn the displeasure of Allah. If Allah wills, He will punish them. If He wills, He will forgive them.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dai